The '''1985 Monte Carlo Open''' (also known as the '''Jacomo Monte Carlo Open''' for sponsorship reasons) was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]] at the [[Monte Carlo Country Club]] in [[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]] that was part of the [[1985 Nabisco Grand Prix]].<ref name="info"/> The tournament was held from 1 April through 7 April 1985.<ref name="info"/>

