[[Image:POL Łódź flag.svg|thumb|right|150px|Flag of Łódź]]
The '''flag of [[Łódź]]''' features the two [[heraldry|heraldic]] [[Tincture (heraldry)|tinctures]] of the '''coat of arms of Łódź''': [[Or (heraldry)|or]] over [[gules]]. In the centre the coat of arms itself appears, depicting a boat, since ''łódź'' in [[Polish language|Polish]] means "boat".

