The '''Ljubljana Summer Festival''' is a festival held between July and August in [[Ljubljana]], the capital of [[Slovenia]].

It attracts notable [[opera]] stars, [[ballet]] and [[theatre]] performers and also eminent [[rock music|rock]] and [[jazz]] musicians internationally who perform at the festival.

