{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2013}} {{Infobox radio station | name = Radio BA | image = [[File:Logo of Radio BA.png|175px|Official logo]] | city = [[Sarajevo]] | area = [[Sarajevo]] | branding = [[Commercial broadcasting|Commercial]] | slogan = '''Radio BA, Sarajevo''' | frequency = [[Sarajevo]] {{Frequency|104.9|[[MHz]]}} | translator = | repeater = | airdate = 2009 | share = | share as of = | share source = | format = [[Contemporary hit radio]], entertainment, talk, news | language = [[Bosnian language]] | power = | erp = | haat = | class = | facility_id = | coordinates = <!-- {{coord|}} --> | callsign_meaning = RADIO BA | former_callsigns = | former_frequencies = <!-- use – --> | affiliations = | owner = "RTV BA" d.o.o. Sarajevo | licensee = | sister_stations = | webcast = On Website | website = {{ URL | http://www.radioba.ba }} }}
'''Radio BA''' is a [[Bosnia]]n commercial radio station, broadcasting from [[Sarajevo]].
'''Radio BA''' was founded during 2009 and the station focuses on [[Contemporary hit radio|contemporary]] pop music, entertainment and local news.<ref name="Radio BA/About us">{{cite web|title=Radio BA/O nama|url=http://www.radioba.ba/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=46&Itemid=37|work= www.radioba.ba|publisher= Radio BA|accessdate=25 August 2013}}</ref> The program is currently broadcast at one frequency ([[Sarajevo]] {{Frequency|104.9|[[MHz]]}}), estimated number of potential listeners is around 443,685.<ref name="Broadcasting / technical requirements for radio stations">{{cite web|title=Tehnički uslovi za radio stanice|url=http://www.cra.ba/bih/index.php?uid=1282977868|work=www.cra.ba|publisher=[[Communications Regulatory Agency of Bosnia and Herzegovina]]|accessdate=25 August 2013}}</ref>
